{"tid":1565488,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「願榮光歸香港」建構香港人《想像的共同體》","createTime":"2019-09-13T07:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T15:28:05.000Z","uid":61886,"like":57,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"26dde5444a5b7d6ba5377d8e064ce19d5eeb773e","tid":1565488,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:19:07.000Z","msg":"《想像的共同體》(Imagined Community)係Benedict Anderson 1983年既作品，大意係講民族係一個大眾想像同埋認知去建構既一個共同體既概念。<br />\n<br />\n咁我語言表達能力較為差，決定搵啲上網既解釋比大家理解依個概念。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就像安德森所指出的，民族之所以...<br />\n&quot;is imagined because the members of even the smallest nation will never know most of their fellow-members, meet them, or even hear of them, yet in the minds of each lives the image of their communion.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n共同體的成員可能永遠不會面對面認識每一個其他成員。然而，他們卻可能有相似的利益，或者識別他們自己為相同民族的一份子。民族成員在他們心中存在親密的心理意象：例如，當你的「想像共同體」參與像是奧林匹克比賽之類的較大型的事件時，你會與你其他的民族成員分享作為同一民族的感覺。 最後，民族是一個共同體，是因為...<br />\n&quot;regardless of the actual inequality and exploitation that may prevail in each, the nation is always conceived as a deep, horizontal comradeship. Ultimately it is this fraternity that makes it possible, over the past two centuries, for so many millions of people, not so much to kill, as willingly to die for such limited imaginings.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n個情況就好似點解北京奧運果時高登仔大叫<br />\n「我係中國人呀屌！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明中國人你一個都唔識<br />\n中國既野又唔關你事<br />\n但都比一個好強烈既影像去渲染到<br />\n令你好自豪成為中國人<br />\n<br />\n而建構一種好強烈既本土民族意識<br />\n係最令中共感到受威脅<br />\n因為當大家有一種好強既香港人意識<br />\n大家就更願意去為香港作出犧牲<br />\n而「願榮光」係可以做到一個好好既推動力<br />\n(亦引證點解中共要每日150大陸西去溝淡真香港人)<br />\n<br />\n所以 <br />\n最近打壓「願榮光」既手段好多<br />\n因為依首歌將我地建構喺同一個共同體之下<br />\n<br />\n可能香港人最後一齊比中共滅族<br />\n可能香港人最後一齊獨立<br />\n但我地之間民族意識愈強<br />\n係百利而無一害<br />\n<br />\nPS <br />\n美國戰線都重要<br />\n我不反對唱美國國歌<br />\n但唔需要一定要揀其中一首唱<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">祈求民主與自由 萬世都不朽<br />\n願榮光歸香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"bb0f69339df2f6a73d7687517b523b26fb4eb479","tid":1565488,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:19:25.000Z","msg":"班門弄斧 勿見怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa595b57ee6094bceacc6f4c2b40d953d1daa3e0","tid":1565488,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:19:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dd9a4HS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdd9a4HS.jpg&h=c9a43637&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"104388d3f0dd9bb9443e3b5b1e7f8b065a03447f","tid":1565488,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:21:15.000Z","msg":"無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTopic係咪太認真？"},{"pid":"9279f5037797f2daa29a790e7ea29c01d808411c","tid":1565488,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:22:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SaiWfQn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSaiWfQn.jpg&h=457e54f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"552f633e266571fe6f058352683bd0524e67e80e","tid":1565488,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:24:33.000Z","msg":"推到收工無人理就算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb06f8e9660f011773df17af6677a96d6cc40e13","tid":1565488,"uid":2607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:25:02.000Z","msg":"一講imagined community 讀書啲野即刻出返黎"},{"pid":"ae3579c6eb1064814bcb5bec151ee84df8137db1","tid":1565488,"uid":131717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:25:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dcd245daf68bae8112cae942b253dc3f76c39f76","tid":1565488,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb06f8e9660f011773df17af6677a96d6cc40e13","tid":1565488,"uid":2607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,